Parsing method: LALR

state 0

    (0) S' -> . program
    (1) program -> . program statement
    (2) program -> . statement
    (3) statement -> . assignment
    (4) assignment -> . ID POW_ASSIGN expression
    (5) assignment -> . ID INT_DIV_ASSIGN expression
    (6) assignment -> . ID PLUS_ASSIGN expression
    (7) assignment -> . ID MINUS_ASSIGN expression
    (8) assignment -> . ID MULT_ASSIGN expression
