    (10) assignment -> . ID MOD_ASSIGN expression
    (11) assignment -> . ID ASSIGN expression

    ID              shift and go to state 4

    program                        shift and go to state 1
    statement                      shift and go to state 2
    assignment                     shift and go to state 3

state 1

